### Create leaderboard
GET {{host}}/api/v1/leaderboards/new

> {%
    client.global.set("secret", response.body.secret);

    client.global.set("lb", response.body.id);
%}


### Create simple score
POST {{host}}/api/v1/scores/{{lb}}/{{secret}}/add/yogurt/1000/
Content-Type: application/json


